{"tid":463700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解支那人咁炫耀自己所謂歷史","createTime":"2017-11-09T17:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T18:58:55.000Z","uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8286fd1c7fab633fc0a63f8b4e0d0c3b4efa4c1d","tid":463700,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"唔好講咩三千年五千年說法<br />\n好多人甚至話支那歷史得一百年<br />\n甚至得幾十年<br />\n<br />\n整部歷史充滿斷斷續續<br />\n被征服被屠殺<br />\n<br />\n支那人 甚至是他們的領袖<br />\n還刻意忽略這些黑歷史向外國人炫耀<br />\n同打飛機有咩分別?"},{"pid":"6eff94b7d0ad2375b44aead276c48d963887991b","tid":463700,"uid":1643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"因為佢地本身冇歷史，夾硬將自己套入去"},{"pid":"8fa464090535761781b1effa9eecb9d1c48ba76c","tid":463700,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"文革先係世界十大笑話<br />\n<br />\n樓主居然冇提"},{"pid":"5d4b5dadd4436fd9835c5843c94d662a13e88303","tid":463700,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為佢地本身冇歷史，夾硬將自己套入去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講埋出口<br />\n隻習總咁樣講知唔知醜<br />\n連戇鳩開既泡菜仔都唔會咁啦"},{"pid":"1fa216a528c2a0a4fa7b0f3b4ecfa35136de5ebe","tid":463700,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文革先係世界十大笑話<br />\n<br />\n樓主居然冇提</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我咪話得幾十年支那歷史"},{"pid":"8f76a6d31c47a8037b5c080b2cc89cc8ff8476f4","tid":463700,"uid":87506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:53:11.000Z","msg":"其實個個國家都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f201156d76d362edb05ca543ea42ebcb5ee4757b","tid":463700,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"有嘅又洗乜去炫耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ce46d4dc44b17c0d546d43a9197331f1cd3c42","tid":463700,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個個國家都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但呢個唔係支那人咁做的借口"},{"pid":"522becee535078b05557bee377a0002176379367","tid":463700,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T18:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有嘅又洗乜去炫耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n愈講愈令人覺得支那人既歷史係吹出黎"}]}